## Common Mistakes

| Mistake | Fix |
|---------|-----|
| Slug mismatch between files | Check PHP filename, `$template_name`, SCSS filename, JS filename, and `HONE_PAGE_TEMPLATES` array — ALL must match |
| Missing `global $class_names` | Must declare at top of template |
| Styles not loading | Check slug is in `HONE_PAGE_TEMPLATES` array |
| JS not loading | Check `wp_enqueue_script('hone-page-' . $template_name)` is called |
| Fonts not rendering | Don't add @font-face — fonts are in main.css |
| Wrong SCSS import path | Use `@use '../variables/colors'` not `@use 'variables/colors'` |
| Styles leaking to other pages | Wrap all styles in `.[slug] { ... }` |
| Images broken | Use `$theme_folder . '/static/media/images/...'` |
| PHP string syntax error | Escape quotes: `'I\'m'` not `'I'm'` |
| Carousel slides invisible | `[aria-hidden="true"] { display: none !important }` is global — add `.slick-slide[aria-hidden="true"] { display: block !important }` in the carousel SCSS |
| Carousel dots show as numbers | `appendDots` generates `.slick-dots li button` with text "1","2"… — style with `font-size: 0; line-height: 0` and `&::before { display: none; }` |
| `accessibility: false` didn't fix aria-hidden | It only disables keyboard nav, not aria attributes. Use the SCSS override instead. |
| New SCSS section nested inside wrong block | After adding a block, run `grep -n "{" file.scss \| tail -20` or check `tail -30` to verify brace structure before building |
| Figma image URLs in PHP | Those expire in 7 days — use `$template_name/filename.webp` with `style="background-color: [hex]"` fallback on the parent |

